  <description>
    <p>Modernised source ports of the flagship idtech4 games: Doom 3, Prey (2006) and Quake 4.</p>
    <p><em>PLEASE NOTE:</em> This Flatpak does <em>not</em> include any game data or CD keys for
        these games. You will need to supply both for any of the games you wish to play.
        At least the <code>*.pk4</code> files from the relevant game data must be copied to
        an appropriate sub-directory in
        <code>$HOME/.var/app/io.github.glkarin.idtech4/[doom3|prey|quake4]/</code>.</p>
    <p>Launching any of the games included will inform you with a message if any of the required
        files are missing and where you need to copy them.</p>
  </description>
